---
---
<section class="relative h-screen min-h-[800px] w-full overflow-hidden bg-[#FAFAF7]">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 flex items-center justify-end">
    <div class="h-full w-full lg:w-3/5">
      <img 
        src="/images/hero.png" 
        alt="Salão de Beleza Premium" 
        class="h-full w-full object-cover opacity-90 grayscale-[20%] transition-transform duration-1000"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FAFAF7] via-[#FAFAF7]/80 to-transparent lg:via-[#FAFAF7]/40"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto flex h-full max-w-7xl items-center px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl reveal">
      <span class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-[#B88746]">
        <span class="h-px w-10 bg-[#B88746]"></span>
        Exclusividade & Arte
      </span>
      
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold leading-[1] text-[#151515] sm:text-8xl italic tracking-tighter text-premium-shadow">
        Redescubra sua <br />
        <span class="text-[#B88746]">Beleza Essencial</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="mt-10 max-w-lg text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#151515]/60 font-medium">
        Uma experiência de cuidado que transcende o espelho. Especialistas dedicados a realçar o seu melhor em um ambiente de absoluto luxo.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-14 flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row">
        <a href="#contato" class="btn-premium px-10">
          Reservar Experiência
        </a>
        <a href="#servicos" class="btn-outline-premium px-10">
          Conhecer Tratamentos
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-6 opacity-40">
        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic">Cabelo</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic">Estética</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic">Bem-estar</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
